data.purpose: UNO MINDA LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 12-Nov-2024 to inter-alia consider and approve the Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the Quarterly ended September 2024 .
To consider and approve the un-audited financial results for the quarter and half year ended on September 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended Jun 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended March 31, 2024 and dividend
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended December 31, 2023 and dividend
